OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774033869
OL,3,CDaughter of North Korean leader Kim
OL,4,CJong Un pictured driving tank
OL,6,FThe teenage daughter of North Korean
OL,7,Fleader Kim Jong Un was pictured
OL,8,Fdriving an anti-drone tank during a
OL,9,Flarge-scale military drill overseen by
OL,10,Fher father.
OL,12,FVideo and images released by state
OL,13,Fmedia on Friday show Kim's daughter
OL,14,Fsticking her head out of the driver's
OL,15,Fhatch of a moving tank, while her
OL,16,Fsmiling father sat on top alongside
OL,17,Fthree soldiers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774033869
OL,3,CDaughter of North Korean leader Kim
OL,4,CJong Un pictured driving tank
OL,6,FThe official Korean Central News
OL,7,FAgency reported that Kim was
OL,8,Foverseeing an offensive tactical drill
OL,9,Finvolving tank units and infantry
OL,10,Ftroops.
OL,12,FThis is the father and daughter's
OL,13,Flatest joint public appearance,
OL,14,Fseemingly supporting outside
OL,15,Fspeculation that the girl, reportedly
OL,16,Fnamed Kim Ju Ae, is groomed as Kim's
OL,17,Fheir.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774033869
OL,3,CDaughter of North Korean leader Kim
OL,4,CJong Un pictured driving tank
OL,6,FObservers say the Jue Ae's position
OL,7,Fclearly shows she was driving the
OL,8,Farmored vehicle. But they note modern
OL,9,Ftanks are not technically complicated
OL,10,Fto pilot, especially while moving
OL,11,Fslowly for a brief time.
OL,13,F"She only drove straight at a low
OL,14,Fspeed. It's also easy to drive modern
OL,15,Ftanks, and I think it was easier for
OL,16,Fher to drive as she was on a flat
OL,17,Fground," said Lee Illwoo, an expert
OL,18,Fwith the Korea Defense Network in
OL,19,FSouth Korea.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
