PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774033869
OL,3,CDaughter of North Korean leader Kim
OL,4,CJong Un pictured driving tank
OL,6,FJue Ae, reportedly aged about 13, has
OL,7,Faccompanied her father to a number of
OL,8,Fhigh-profile military and other events
OL,9,Fsince late 2022.
OL,11,FThe pair recently fired pistols during
OL,12,Fa visit to a light munitions factory
OL,13,Fand watched a live-fire test of
OL,14,Fmultiple rocket launch systems.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
