FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774033869
OL,3,CDaughter of North Korean leader Kim
OL,4,CJong Un pictured driving tank
OL,6,FNorth Korean state media has called
OL,7,Fher Kim's "most beloved" or
OL,8,F"respected" child and published
OL,9,Ffootage and photos indicating the
OL,10,Ftwo's closeness. It is believed that
OL,11,Fthe North Korean leader has two other
OL,12,Fchildren.
OL,14,FSouth Korea's spy agency assessed last
OL,15,Fmonth that Kim was close to
OL,16,Fdesignating her as his heir.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
